&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/3238&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/3238&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

